  <title>Add a Bonding Parameter</title>
  <shortdesc>To add a bonding parameter:</shortdesc>
  <body>
    <ol>
      <li>Edit the host in the Foreman interface.</li>
      <li>Select the <b>Parameters</b> tab.</li>
      <li>Click the <b>+ Add Parameter</b> button to create new parameters.</li>
    </ol>
  </body>
